    "body": "The fix in #267 allows specifying the timeouts per network.\n\nFor instance:\n\n```\nnetworks: {\n        \"morden\": {\n            network_id: 2,            \n            host: \"localhost\",\n            port: 8546,\n            before_timeout: 200000,          //  <=== NEW\n            test_timeout: 300000             //  <=== NEW\n        },\n        \"dev\": {\n            network_id: \"default\",\n            before_timeout: 300,             //  <=== NEW\n            test_timeout: 300                //  <=== NEW\n        }\n    }\n```\n",
